<?xml version="1.0"?>
<package >
  <metadata>
    <id>WPFNotification</id>
    <version>1.1.0</version>
    <title>Toast Notification for WPF</title>
    <authors>Muhammed Magdy</authors>
    <owners>Muhammed Magdy</owners>
    <description>
      Fancy toast notification for WPF applications easy to use and support MVVM pattern. A small notification window with image, title and content displayed at the bottom of the screen. You can use the default implementation or build your own custom notification.Notifications added to a buffer queue then each notification appears after the previous notification disappeared or closed.Support windows 7 or later and different screen resolution
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>
      V1.0.2 Adds support for windows 7 or later.
      Adds support for displaying notification on different screen resolutions.
      Add Notification Flow Direction,That Set direction in which new notifications will appear. Available options are:
      * RightBottom (default)
      * LeftBottom
      * LeftUp
      * RightUp
      Add Clear notification feature, that Remove all notifications from the notification list and the buffer list.
      V1.0.3 Add Package Dependencies
      V1.1.0 Remove dependency on System.Reactive.* dlls
    </releaseNotes>
    <summary>
      Fancy Toast notification for WPF applications.
    </summary>
